ing: 1 (16 ounce) package kielbasa sausage, sliced into 1/2 inch pieces
des: "This easy appetizer is perfect for your pre-game football tailgating parties or other special occasions."
ins: Pour the ketchup and barbecue sauce into a slow cooker. Stir in the brown sugar, whiskey, and sausage. Set on Low, and cook for 6 hours. Serve hot with toothpicks.
